Class User

java.lang.Object
model.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
The User class contains information about a user, including their username, their albums, their tag types, and more.
Author:
Seok Yim, Mae Khaled
